com.lambdaworks.redis.cluster.api.async

Interface AsyncNodeSelection<K,V>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NodeSelectionSupport<RedisAsyncCommands<K,V>,NodeSelectionAsyncCommands<K,V>>

    public interface AsyncNodeSelection<K,V>
extends NodeSelectionSupport<RedisAsyncCommands<K,V>,NodeSelectionAsyncCommands<K,V>>
    Node selection with access to asynchronous executed commands on the set. This API is subject to incompatible changes in a future release. The API is exempt from any compatibility guarantees made by lettuce. The current state implies nothing about the quality or performance of the API in question, only the fact that it is not "API-frozen." The NodeSelection command API and its result types are a base for discussions.
    Since:
    4.0
    Author:
    Mark Paluch
